room_title: Escape room "CSI: Crime Scene Investigation" by Twisted Key Escape Room in Dallas-Fort Worth
room_address: 201 NE Wilshire Blvd Suite D Burleson, TX 76028
room_description: Phillip Cleabourne, a self made millionaire and philanthropist that loves to travel the world collecting obscure items, has been murdered and you have been called in to investigate. You are a trainee trying to get on the force and need to impress Detective Spade in order to get his recommendation. Are you sleuth enough to solve the case?
